data.title: LOCAL CANDIDATES AND COMMITTEES
meta_keywords: Flagler County Local Candidates and Committees
data.meta_description: Flagler County Local Candidates and Committees
data.text:
All local candidates in Flagler County are listed on this page. To view Federal and state candidates, please refer to the list of General Election Candidates for upcoming elections which is compiled by the Florida Division of Elections. City of Palm Coast candidates and some City of Bunnell candidates are using electronic reporting, you can view their financial information here. Other municipal candidates are listed here for reference, but their financial reports are filed with their respective City Clerk: Beverly Beach, Bunnell, Flagler Beach. Circuit judges qualify and file their financial reports with the Florida Division of Elections, they are listed here for reference.
